segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia's growing up. Another's on the way.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: No, Fugui's signature is on each one.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: Long'er, is our Xu family home...
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text:
A gambling debt's a debt,
and debts must be paid.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: I'll look after her for a few days?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: Master Fugui! It's been a year at least.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: My heart is full of sorrow
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: He hadn't slept for three days.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: Let's not bring up the past.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text:
Burn them, okay?
I've got other people to see.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text:
I just came from the hospital.
The doctor says it's due in autumn.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia's going to be a mother.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: He's been arrested as a capitalist.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: They held a public trial against him.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04

segmentosSRT.text: We have to draw a line between us and him.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_04
